    "stdyInfo": {
      "abstract": [
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "HYPOCRAS est destinée à évaluer « en vie réelle » le risque hypoglycémique des inhibiteurs de la dipeptidylpeptidase IV (iDPP4) versus autres antidiabétiques oraux (AADO) en addition à la metformine chez des patients âgés diabétiques de type 2 (DT2)"
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "HYPOCRAS aims to compare hypoglycaemic risk in dipeptidyl peptidase-4 inhibitors (iDPP4s) with other oral antidiabetic drugs (OAD) along with metaformin in the real-life treatment of elderly patients with type 2 diabetes (T2D)."
        }
      ],
